<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            color: #182444;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .code-box {
            background-color: #ffcc00;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: rgb(4, 33, 63);
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255)878;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bolder;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .course-link {
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://your-logo-url.png" alt="Pathshala Logo" class="logo">
        <div class="header">Welcome to Pathshala!</div>
        <h2>Hello ,<span style="color:#182444; font-weight: bolder; text-transform: capitalize;"><%= user.name %></span></h2>
        <p class="message">Your activation code:</p>
        <div class="code-box"><%= activationCode %></div>
        <p class="message">This code will be valid for only 5 minutes.</p>
        <p class="message">Thank you for registering with Pathshala! Wish you a great e-learning experience.</p>
        <a href="https://your-pathshala-url.com" class="btn" target="_blank">Explore Courses</a>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Follow us on <a href="https://twitter.com/pathshala" target="_blank">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://facebook.com/pathshala" target="_blank">Facebook</a> for updates!</p>
            <p>Pathshala - Your Learning Companion</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
